<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Demystifying Ripple&#8217;s Lightning-Fast Transaction Capabilities</h2>



<p>Let&#8217;s take a closer look at the mechanics behind XRP&#8217;s rapid settlements and how it compares to traditional payment rails in terms of speed.</p>



