<p>As you explore the significance of XRP Ledger&#8217;s close times in real-world applications, it&#8217;s important to consider the impact of its rapid transaction processing. The close times of the XRP Ledger refer to the speed at which transactions are confirmed and added to the ledger.</p>



<p>Here are four reasons why the close times of the XRP Ledger are significant in real-world applications:</p>



