<figure class="wp-block-table"><table><thead><tr><th>Scalability Innovations</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>XRP Ledger Consensus Protocol</td><td>A unique consensus algorithm that enables fast and secure transaction confirmation.</td></tr><tr><td>High-speed transaction processing engine</td><td>Allows Ripple to handle up to 1,500 transactions per second.</td></tr><tr><td>Improved network infrastructure</td><td>Ripple has invested in improving its network infrastructure to enhance scalability and performance.</td></tr><tr><td>Advanced data compression techniques</td><td>By implementing advanced data compression techniques, Ripple has reduced the size of transaction data, resulting in faster processing times.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



