<li><strong>Enhanced efficiency: </strong>Faster transaction speeds allow for quicker processing of transactions, reducing the time and effort required to complete a transaction. This makes it easier and more convenient for you to send and receive funds, improving overall efficiency.</li>



<li><strong>Increased security:</strong> Faster transactions reduce the time window during which potential security threats can occur. This enhances the security of your digital assets and minimizes the risk of fraudulent activities.</li>



<li><strong>Better user experience:</strong> Waiting for transactions to be confirmed can be frustrating. Faster transaction speeds eliminate this waiting time, providing you with a seamless and smooth user experience.</li>
</ol>



